546
00:35:08,029 --> 00:35:11,157
- Get real.
- It really wouldn't matter to me.

547
00:35:11,240 --> 00:35:13,409
- Whatever.
- It's true.

548
00:35:13,534 --> 00:35:16,954
Once you've had money all of your life,
