560
00:35:54,617 --> 00:35:57,870
Well, obviously we're people.
Standard issue street soldiers.

561
00:35:58,037 --> 00:36:01,874
Standard issue street soldiers.

562
00:36:01,958 --> 00:36:06,629
- That's a great tag line.
- Thanks. Came up with that myself.

563
00:36:08,256 --> 00:36:10,174
So why do you hate your stepmom?

564
00:36:10,258 --> 00:36:12,343
What makes you think I do?

565
00:36:13,970 --> 00:36:16,764
- Just a hunch.
- She's a twit.

566
00:36:16,889 --> 00:36:20,643
