622
00:40:16,337 --> 00:40:19,298
I always liked the cowboy the best.

623
00:40:19,382 --> 00:40:21,592
Domino's Pizza!

624
00:40:21,676 --> 00:40:25,096
- Jack, it's me, Ari.
- It's my lawyer.

625
00:40:25,179 --> 00:40:27,723
- Jack?
- Ari, I told you never to call me here.

626
00:40:27,849 --> 00:40:30,935
Jack, this is wrong.
This is very, very wrong.

627
00:40:31,018 --> 00:40:32,937
I mean, I know you're disappointed.

628
00:40:33,020 --> 00:40:36,232
Disappointed? How about destroyed, Ari?
How about devastated?

629
00:40:36,357 --> 00:40:40,153
- Jack, this is not the way to beat the system.
- Screw the system.

630
00:40:40,236 --> 00:40:42,196
No, not screw the system.

631
