you dealin' with the scum of the Earth.

666
00:42:44,277 --> 00:42:47,947
The only people you come in contact
with are dope pushers...

667
00:42:48,030 --> 00:42:51,492
and pimps and killers
and child molesters.

668
00:42:51,576 --> 00:42:54,245
