675
00:43:20,188 --> 00:43:22,899
Tell you what, Jer.
You let your viewers know...

676
00:43:23,024 --> 00:43:26,444
that I hope Miss Voss's fear
and my desperation...

677
00:43:26,527 --> 00:43:28,446
are entertainment enough for them.

678
00:43:28,529 --> 00:43:31,449
After all, that's what
this is all about, right?

679
00:43:31,532 --> 00:43:33,534
What makes for good television?

680
00:43:33,618 --> 00:43:37,830
